channel.title: 2012 Venus Transit
channel.description: A few images from the 2012 Venus Transit event.

item.title: Setup for the 2012 transit of Venus. 6/5/12.
item.description: The setup for the 2012 transit of Venus, ready to go. The 6-inch reflector is used to project the Sun, while the sun funnel refractor piggybacks on the 12-inch.

item.title: Guests at the transit of Venus event. June 2012.
item.description: Observatory guests stand underneath the retracted roof, waiting for their turn to view the transit of Venus. June 2012.
